Slide 10 of 20 - HRA Reporting Requirements




Slide notes
This final example involves an RRE that is reporting HRA coverage where the Plan year starts November 1, 2010.
If the RRE’s regular reporting month is October, they cannot report the record in the October report because the
Effective Date of November 1, 2010 would be a future date. Future Effective Dates are not permitted.
The RRE should report the HRA coverage record with the MSP Input File they submit in their first Quarter of
2011.
If the RRE’s regular 4th Quarter reporting month is either November or December, the HRA coverage should be
reported with their 4th Quarter report.




