Slide 11 of 20 - HRA Reporting Requirements New Enrollees




Slide notes
New enrollees should be reported as soon as possible after their Effective Date.
Recall however, CMS does not consider a record to be submitted late if the Effective Date of the HRA plan is
within the 45-day period prior to the RRE’s assigned submission period and the record is not reported in that
period.
The record may be submitted in the next scheduled Benefits Coordination & Recovery Center (BCRC) assigned
reporting period.




