Slide 15 of 20 - HRA Reporting Requirements Annual Benefit Value




Slide notes
HRAs with an annual benefit amount of less than $5,000 are exempt from reporting. Only HRA coverage that
reflects an annual benefit value of $5,000 or more must be reported.




