Slide 16 of 20 - HRA Reporting Requirements Annual Benefit Value




Slide notes
Due to carry-over or roll-over options in an HRA, if the value of the HRA starts at less than $5,000 but grows to
meet or exceed $5,000, the HRA must be reported when the increase to $5,000 or more occurs.




